                    <span id="c-1144991627" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1144991627" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1144991627">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/qiansuiyou/">如是我闻</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-02-01</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">有了理论，我们就能够把本质与迷人的外表和偶然的特性区分开来。理论给我们提供了前进的路标，使我们明白要观察些什么以及该怎么做。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="137985079">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-137985079" class="vote-count">0</span>
